      "value": "<p><strong>Level 4</strong> Divination</p>\n<p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action</p>\n<p><strong>Range:</strong> 30 feet</p>\n<p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S, M (a bit of bat fur)</p>\n<p><strong>Duration:</strong> Concentration, up to 1 hour</p>\n\nYou create an Invisible|XPHB, invulnerable eye within range that hovers for the duration. You mentally receive visual information from the eye, which can see in every direction. It also has Darkvision|XPHB with a range of 30 feet. As a Bonus Action|XPHB, you can move the eye up to 30 feet in any direction. A solid barrier blocks the eye's movement, but the eye can pass through an opening as small as 1 inch in diameter.",
